{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-archived-blog-template-js","path":"/2015/05/the-voice/","result":{"data":{"archivedBlogPostJson":{"categories":[{"path":"/category/entertainment/","name":"生活娱乐活动"}],"tags":[{"name":"唐城","path":"/tag/tang-city/"},{"name":"大楚网","path":"/tag/dachu/"},{"name":"好声音","path":"/tag/good-voice/"},{"name":"襄阳","path":"/tag/xiangyang/"}],"featured_media":{"source_url":"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/tangcheng.jpg"},"path":"/2015/05/the-voice/","date":"2015-05-28T10:51:49.000Z","excerpt":"2015-05-17，中国好声音湖北地区独家网络招募-襄阳-试音活动，在活动的尾声也是最高潮我参与到其中。 我 … ","title":"一场幕后比台前更有故事与戏剧化的活动","content":"<p><embed src=\"//static.video.qq.com/TPout.swf?vid=m0155jxssme&amp;auto=0\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"480\" height=\"400\" align=\"middle\"/></p>\n<p>2015-05-17，中国好声音湖北地区独家网络招募-襄阳-试音活动，在活动的尾声也是最高潮我参与到其中。</p>\n<p>我带领红队组员们热情的投入其中，队员们每人都很棒，我也很开心！</p>\n<p>原本计划的活动因为人为和天气的因素而未执行，这短片也无故事内容可讲了，只能看个热闹。不过幕后发生的一些戏剧化的事情，更是有趣，笑笑得了！</p>\n<p>第一次剪辑航拍的素材。</p>\n<p><figure id=\"attachment_1770\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1770\" style=\"width: 1200px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_9306_2.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-1770\" src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_9306_2.jpg\" alt=\"这衣服帽子搭配还不错！\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_9306_2.jpg 1200w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_9306_2-300x200.jpg 300w, https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_9306_2-864x576.jpg 864w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 89vw, (max-width: 1000px) 54vw, (max-width: 1071px) 543px, 580px\" /></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1770\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">这衣服帽子搭配还不错！</figcaption></figure></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2015/05/the-voice/"}},"staticQueryHashes":